---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import Layout from "../../layouts/2024Layout.astro";
import TampaHacks2024 from "../../assets/tampahacks-2024.jpeg";
---

<Layout>
  <hr class="my-5 w-1/2 bg-white" />
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-5">
    <Image
      src={TampaHacks2024}
      alt="TampaHacks 2024"
      class="w-4/5 rounded-md md:w-2/5"
    />
    <p class="w-4/5 text-center text-2xl text-white md:w-1/2">
      TampaHacks was great! We had around 9 students from the Tampa Bay area and
      beyond come and make some amazing games at <a
        href="https://amroctampabay.com/"
        class="underline">AMRoC Fab Lab</a
      > on August 17th, 2024.
    </p>
    <p class="w-4/5 text-center text-2xl text-white md:w-1/2">
      This event was organized by 3 high schoolers in Tampa: <a
        href="https://github.com/Luke-Oldenburg/"
        class="underline">Luke Oldenburg</a
      >, <a href="https://sfernandez.dev" class="underline">Samuel Fernandez</a
      >, and <a href="https://github.com/ultimatehecker" class="underline"
        >ultimate_hecker</a
      >. This was the first event of its kind in the Tampa Bay area, but
      definitely not the last.
    </p>
    <p class="w-4/5 text-center text-2xl text-white md:w-1/2">
      If you'd like to be notified about future events and announcements, please
      sign up for our newsletter on our <a
        href="https://lu.ma/tampahacks"
        class="underline">Luma calendar</a
      >.
    </p>
    <div
      class="my-5 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-x-10 md:flex-row"
    >
      <a
        class="block rounded-md border-2 border-sky-800 bg-sky-500 px-5 py-3 text-center text-2xl font-bold text-white"
        href="https://lu.ma/tampahacks"
      >
        Luma Calendar
      </a>
      <a
        class="block px-5 py-3 text-center text-2xl font-bold text-white underline"
        href="/2024/launch"
      >
        See pre-event website
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="my-5 w-1/2 bg-white" />
</Layout>
